spec_data.Name: perl-Directory-Scratch-Structured
spec_data.Description:
This module adds a _create_structured_tree_ subroutine to Directory::Scratch.
This method is useful to create a directory structure needed for temporary
purposes, e.g. for testing.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:09:59 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Creates temporary files and directories from a structured description
